{
  "texts": [
    "To generate these DNNs with varying architectures and input sizes, there exist several techniques, such as bag-of-models (Han et al. 2016), early-exit (Laskaridis et al. 2020a), and neural architecture search (Cai et al. 2020).",
    "We leverage the bag-ofmodels foot_1 technique to select a list of pretrained DNNs.",
    "We sort DNNs in increasing order of their input sizes.",
    "After sorting, we expect the accuracies of these DNNs to follow an increasing order; otherwise, we simply remove the DNNs with lower accuracy but a larger input size.",
    "We profile (and store) the latency and accuracy of these DNNs for different batch sizes."
  ]
}